UNITED STATES ex rel. Joseph WENGER, Appellant, v. W. Frank MATHUES, U. S. Marshal Appellee. * Circuit Court of Appeals, Third Circuit. December 10,1928. No. 3854. William A. Gray, of Philadelphia, Pa., for appellant. Elmer C. Pfeiffer, of Philadelphia, Pa., for appellee.

Before BUFFINGTON, WOOLLEY, and DAVIS, Circuit Judges.

Appeal dismissed 49 S. Ct. —, 73 L. Ed. —,

 PER CURIAM.

Finding no error in the order of the court below, directing removal, it is affirmed.
